Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我需要帮忙  我就张口了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If I needed a hand, I'd ask for it --
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-给您  女士  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- There you go, miss. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.31,0:00:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽恩  你好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Marion. How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:01:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么回事吧  脑子还好使\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Could be worse. Brain's still working.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天来点五香熏牛肉吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is it a pastrami day?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-要  只要一斤一两  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah. Uh, one and a quarter pounds. - You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一斤四两  你上次称多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not a pound and a half, you overshot last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.86,0:01:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sorry 'bout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do we have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特干威斯康辛切达奶酪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Extra-sharp Wisconsin cheddar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特干\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Extra-sharp," Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可算了吧  威斯康辛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can keep it, Wisconsin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前来的时候不是这样的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It wasn't like this when I came before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要帮忙吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Need some help?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.91,0:02:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确定不需要推一下吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you sure you don't want a push?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}我叫咬咬  你见过我吗  请打402-432-9288
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小咬咬怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What happened to poor Nippy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开车的时候开着车窗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was driving with the windows open,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时还没下雪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you know, before all this hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道  什么东西吸引了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And -- I don't know -- something got into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看见小猫之类的了  跳了出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He saw a cat or something -- but he jumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我立刻停车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I pulled right over,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大喊着"咬咬"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}screaming my head off, "Nippyyyy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  他跑了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But...he was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, that's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能找到他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I hope you find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.24,0:02:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托帮忙留意一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you could keep an eye out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  肯定的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I will. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:02:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在这住  在克莱门汀街\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I-I live right over here on -- on Clementine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就走这条路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is my route.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我把这破玩意开起来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When I can get this thing going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是稍微推一下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe just a little push.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不介意的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, if you're sure you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐意帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nah. I'm happy to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  挂到空挡上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay. Throw it in neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  三\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And one, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.41,0:03:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉添麻烦了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂回行驶挡  不用客气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Put it back in drive. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-祝你开心  -你也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Have a nice day. - Yeah, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能找到咬咬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hope you find Nippy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还行吗  玛丽恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How ya doing, Marion?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好极了  -那就好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Great. - Ah, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你可以吧  -没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Are you okay? - Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}绝命律师\N第六季第十集
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}阿尔布开克同位素棒球队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实  这是我的拿手好菜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Actually, it's my favorite meal to cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我喜欢  -我的秘诀就是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I like it. - And I think my secret is --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ma?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在厨房  杰夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In the kitchen, Jeffie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个秘诀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have a little trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我敢肯定跟我家一个做法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I bet it's the same we do in my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-加个蛋  -我就知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- An egg. - I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要搅拌均匀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you really work it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要用手抓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, you got to use your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You are speaking my language.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你下厨吗  -就几个家常菜  不做什么大餐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Do you cook? - Just a few favorites, nothing fancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单最好了  何必麻烦呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, simple's best. I mean, why fuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰夫  这位是塔卡维奇先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jeffie, this is Mr. Takavic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲才叫塔卡维奇先生呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, please, Mr. Takavic was my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我吉恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Call me "Gene."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心  孩子  他不是什么斧子杀手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't worry, hon, he's not an ax murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要是想砍了我  他早就动手了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If he was gonna chop me to bits he'd have done it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  吉恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right, Gene?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在那傻站着了  快一起坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, don't just stand there like a bump on a log, join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候他见到生人有点紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sometimes he gets a little nervous around new people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-妈  -本来嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Ma. - Well, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿个杯子坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Grab a glass and sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他讲讲我们怎么认识的  吉恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tell him how we met, Gene.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我正在找咬咬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, well, I was looking for Nippy --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  他的狗  小可怜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. His dog, poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跑丢了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, he ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉恩当时正在贴寻狗启事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And Gene here was putting up posters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲刚好从汉森超市回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And your mom was on her way back from Hansen's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的轮子卡在雪里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And my wheels got stuck in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后助力车整个坏掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, that was before the whole thing conked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  但是吉恩今天就是大救星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, but Gene here saved the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还用强力胶带修好了我的破车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He even fixed my dumb scooter -- with duct tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-敬吉恩  -别客气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- To Gene. - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲说你是出租车司机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So your mom tells me you're a cab driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你载过什么名人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you ever driven anyone famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, he sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他讲讲  杰夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tell him, Jeffie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨米·海格\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sammy Hagar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧  "红色摇滚乐手"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No! The Red Rocker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,♪ 我不能超速55迈 ♪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}♪ I can't drive 55 ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这首\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人怎么样  大方吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What was he like? Big tipper?
