Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼克  我好像闻到肉桂卷的香味了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nick! Do I detect Cinnabons?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你还不快让他进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, Christ almighty, get him in here.
