Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.80,0:26:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得能行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think it'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.33,0:26:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.75,0:26:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很年轻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're young.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.35,0:27:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计跑得快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're probably, uh, fast on the feet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.71,0:27:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我没说我不干\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, I-I didn't say I wouldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.00,0:27:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是有点关于后勤的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just had some questions about, like, logistics.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.09,0:27:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底干不干\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you in or out?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.90,0:27:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.12,0:27:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.98,0:27:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Back to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.73,0:27:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  一二  一二\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Check, test, one, two, one, two.
