Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.54,0:27:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Move! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.58,0:27:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚步快点  快快快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pick up the pace! Go! Go! Go!
