Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.18,0:27:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六  时髦运动服随意搭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Six! Swanky sweatsuits in the mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.78,0:27:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑快跑快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's go! Let's go! Let's go!
