Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.45,0:28:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.83,0:28:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, then. Have a good night.
