Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.83,0:28:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Excuse me, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.53,0:28:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有货物送到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's a delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.54,0:28:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,货物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A delivery?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.46,0:28:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.15,0:28:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.23,0:28:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.63,0:28:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能把它留在我的装卸口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You are not leaving that thing on my loading dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.79,0:28:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.17,0:28:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棉白杨大道1412号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fourteen twelve Cottonwood Drive...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.66,0:28:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D装卸口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dock -- Dock D.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.17,0:28:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.96,0:28:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二冲程发动机喷雾泵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Two-stroke engine sprayer pumps?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.41,0:28:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是百货商场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is a department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.74,0:28:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我们用得上喷雾泵吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Does it look like we use sprayer pumps here?
