Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.69,0:29:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟你的上级通话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I need to talk to your supervisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.26,0:29:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  你待着别动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Got it. You stay right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.15,0:29:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调度中心  史蒂夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dispatch. Steve.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.71,0:29:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是凯茜·德驰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes -- this is Kathy Deutsch,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.19,0:29:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是奥马哈市一家兰开斯特百货的经理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm the manager of a Lancaster's in Omaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.66,0:29:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们送来了一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you guys just delivered something
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.88,0:29:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我们没订的东西  -是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- that we did not order. - Really?
