Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.87,0:29:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  稍等一下我捋捋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, just, uh, give me a second to catch up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.07,0:29:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喷雾泵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh... Uh, sprayer pump.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.02,0:29:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I think I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.34,0:29:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥马哈  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Omaha, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.12,0:29:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  但我们是百货公司\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, but I run a department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.03,0:29:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不卖喷雾泵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We don't sell anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.89,0:29:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个错误你得解决\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Clearly this is a mistake you need to fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.99,0:30:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊  真抱歉  女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, my God. I'm so sorry, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.72,0:30:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的老板会...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My boss is gonna just...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.10,0:30:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下可好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ah, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.29,0:30:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞奇的时间都排满了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ricky's booked solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.09,0:30:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ricky?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.05,0:30:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是司机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.85,0:30:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞奇把箱子搬回卡车上就行了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, Ricky's just gonna have to put the box back on the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.56,0:30:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有点问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, little problem with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.00,0:30:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,载货空间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cargo space.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.22,0:30:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一小时后要在机场接货\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's got a pickup at the airport in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.59,0:30:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也很麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a messy one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.96,0:30:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,408公斤西班牙鲭鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's, uh, nine hundred pounds of Spanish mackerel.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.29,0:30:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  很遗憾  但这不是我的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay. I'm sorry, but that's not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.01,0:30:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实  我知道  就是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, I know. It's just -- Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.78,0:30:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他迟到了  鱼就臭了{\fs14}[就坏事了]{\fs}\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, if he's late, that's gonna stink.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.73,0:30:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是双关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pun intended.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.78,0:30:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉恩  还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gene? Everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.05,0:30:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我就是在处理紧急情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yep. Oh, I'm just, uh, putting out fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.19,0:30:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送货问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a delivery issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.70,0:30:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-别担心  -好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Don't worry. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.60,0:30:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能处理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.26,0:30:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.46,0:30:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你还在听吗  -在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You still there? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.93,0:30:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于你的鱼问题  我不知道该说些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, I don't know what to tell you about your fish issue,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.97,0:30:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过我不能让这么大个箱子...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it's just I can't have a huge box just --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.33,0:30:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I-I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.46,0:31:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just -- I mean, we both have people
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.09,0:31:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都只是个打工的  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we have to answer to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.80,0:31:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个主意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, I've got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.45,0:31:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有辆车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Um, I've got an extra truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.62,0:31:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以亲自开过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I could drive over there myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.58,0:31:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好  你多久能到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Great. How long till you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.14,0:31:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在还在厄本代尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I'm just over in Urbandale.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.77,0:31:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  如果我现在出发  四个小时能到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Um, so, if I leave right now, be there in four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.45,0:31:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四个小时  不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Four hours? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.53,0:31:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  没事  没关系  这点车程没什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no, it's fine. I don't mind the drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.38,0:31:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找几首歌路上听  就像以前一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll crank the tunes, it'll be like old times.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.70,0:31:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是指我等不了那么久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, no, I can't wait around that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.43,0:31:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要打烊了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're closing for the night here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.93,0:31:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不这么着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.32,0:31:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.72,0:31:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能保证...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you promise me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.77,0:31:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞奇明早十点之前能回来...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ricky will get back here by 10:00 a.m. tomorrow...
