Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.38,0:31:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意通融吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You would do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.10,0:31:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊  你真是我的大恩人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, my God. You're a lifesaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.16,0:31:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么来着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.49,0:31:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-凯茜  -凯茜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Kathy. - Kathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.44,0:31:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言为定  我的人早上十点一定准时到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, my guy'll be there, 10:00 a.m. on the dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.34,0:31:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上鲜花聊表心意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}With flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.03,0:32:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花就不必了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, f-flowers won't be necessary...
