Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.69,0:40:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是很重要的存在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to a lot of -- lots of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.29,0:40:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我今晚死了  我房东会帮我收拾东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If I died tonight, my landlord would pack up my stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.29,0:40:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就占用他三个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It'd take him three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.72,0:40:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而辛纳邦也会雇个新店长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And Cinnabon would just hire a new manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.66,0:40:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉恩是哪位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gene who?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.04,0:40:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗖的一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Poof!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.31,0:40:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就消失不见了  我会变成...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd be gone. I'd be...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.66,0:40:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.08,0:40:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个鬼魂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.21,0:40:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼魂都算不上  我会变成一个影子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Less than a ghost. I'd be a -- a sha-- shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.60,0:40:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd just be...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.54,0:40:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.55,0:40:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰克  这有什么意义呢  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, Frank -- what's the point, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.15,0:40:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意义何在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's the poi--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.90,0:41:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, you -- I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.84,0:41:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你听我发牢骚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You didn't need to hear any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.40,0:41:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no, no, no, no, that's -- that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.49,0:41:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, that -- that is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.18,0:41:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都有不开心的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everybody has bad days.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.28,0:41:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有过这种感觉吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've felt like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.41,0:41:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒没有  但总有人有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, I mean, not me -- but people.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.17,0:41:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多人都会有这种感觉的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I-I think a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.81,0:41:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像人生总是起起伏伏的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I mean, I-it's just like life's ups and life's downs.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.47,0:41:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.13,0:41:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会跟尼克说的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, you're not gonna tell Nick, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.31,0:41:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, 'course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.72,0:41:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你听我倒苦水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well...thanks so much for listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.31,0:41:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  小事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, no, no. No p-- No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.20,0:43:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不确定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.32,0:43:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色或者黑色吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm thinking maybe blue or black?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.78,0:43:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么场合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's the occasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.07,0:43:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐妹的婚礼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My sister's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.34,0:43:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, very exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.33,0:43:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您穿什么尺码的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Um, what size are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.65,0:43:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般是38或者40的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Usually a 38 or a 40?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.29,0:43:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两件都试试怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you want to try both?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.55,0:43:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.35,0:43:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生  有什么需要吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sir, do you need help?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.99,0:43:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.42,0:43:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有事找那边的芭芭拉就行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, Barbara's right here if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.74,0:43:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-凯茜  是这件吗  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Kathy, is this it? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.76,0:43:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了女士  取大箱子的货车到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Excuse me, ma'am? Truck's here to pick up that big box.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.14,0:43:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Great, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.90,0:43:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人还送了花\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh... the guy brought flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.67,0:43:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.13,0:44:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-快看  -美得很\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Look. - Ooh la la! Ooh la la!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.44,0:44:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧这件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.12,0:44:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士们早啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Buongiorno, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.79,0:44:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这些能卖多少钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How much you think we can get for 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.02,0:44:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  每件大概五百块吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know. Maybe...five hundred each?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.71,0:44:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但说真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But shit, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.98,0:44:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我干脆留着自己穿好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe I just keep 'em for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.69,0:44:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我眼馋这几双球鞋很久了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've been eyeing these Jordans.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.33,0:44:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们很爽吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You guys enjoying yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.71,0:44:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就记住这种感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, hold onto that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.91,0:44:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为到此为止了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Cause this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.59,0:44:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.93,0:44:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕你们忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, in case you forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.48,0:44:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们转运了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You transported stolen goods
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.80,0:44:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,价格超过五千美元的赃物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with a value exceeding five thousand dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.88,0:44:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们开的货车是从州界旁的康瑟尔布拉夫斯市\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And the truck you used to do it was rented in Council Bluffs,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.86,0:44:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,租用的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}across state lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.92,0:44:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你叫我们在那里租的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You told us to rent the truck over there --
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.63,0:45:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,州际运输失窃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Theft from an Interstate Shipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.16,0:45:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最多能判十年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Up to ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.92,0:45:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转运赃物  又判十年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Transportation of Stolen Goods. Another ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.21,0:45:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,销售赃物  再加十年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sale of Stolen Goods. Ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.11,0:45:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合谋犯下联邦罪行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Conspiracy to commit a federal crime --
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.37,0:45:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合谋  这是你的主意好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Conspiracy"? It was your idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.81,0:45:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没错  这叫"相互保证毁灭"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. It's called "Mutually assured destruction."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.07,0:45:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是出事了  也会拉着你们同归于尽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, if I go down, you go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.23,0:45:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用威胁我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Man, you don't have to threaten us.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.55,0:45:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是朋友一场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're all friends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.83,0:45:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是你们的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am not your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.66,0:45:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要是掉钱眼里了  还想回来再干一票\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And if you get greedy and you decide
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.32,0:45:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我劝你打消这个念头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to come back for more, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.18,0:45:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉恩·塔卡维奇  你们从没听说过这个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gene Takavic -- you never heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.32,0:45:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棉白杨商场  你们再也别去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Cottonwood Mall? You don't go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.66,0:45:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上见到我了  就过个马路绕着我走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You see me coming, you cross to the other side of the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.88,0:45:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老兄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dude --
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.61,0:45:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都照着我的说  "我们洗手不干了"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now I need you to say it: "We're done."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.87,0:45:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-干啥呢  -快说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Come on! - Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.68,0:45:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我们洗手不干了"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"We're. Done."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.20,0:45:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.30,0:46:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们洗手不干了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.59,0:46:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们...洗手不干了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're -- We're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.48,0:46:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gene?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.47,0:46:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉恩  我看见你的车了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, Gene, I see your car!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.87,0:46:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gene?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.28,0:46:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之开了个头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, that's a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.95,0:46:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来问题出在制动主缸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Looks like your problem is the master cylinder.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.90,0:46:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧你们  正在卖力干活呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look at you boys, hard at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.87,0:46:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽恩  两位  我得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, Marion, guys, I got to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.14,0:46:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下次来了再帮你看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I will take another look next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.51,0:46:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.25,0:46:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一身脏兮兮的能去哪呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, you can't go anywhere looking like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.69,0:46:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快进屋里洗洗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on inside and wash up.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.18,0:46:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.42,0:46:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰夫  别烦我  快点  吉恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jeffie, don't vex me. Come on, Gene.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.74,0:47:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以帮我放杂货\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can help me with the groceries.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.11,0:47:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-吉恩  -听起来不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Huh, Gene? - Sounds like a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.66,0:47:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帮杰夫修车真好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nice of you to help Jeffie with his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.27,0:47:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也许不知道  我儿子以前过得不太顺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You might not know it, but my boy's had some tough times.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.02,0:47:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在阿尔布开克摊上了一群坏人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He, uh -- He fell in with a bad crowd back in Albuquerque.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.15,0:47:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔布开克  我没去过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Albuquerque, huh? Never been.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.48,0:47:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真走运\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lucky you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.27,0:47:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但杰夫在这里就好多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But things are so much better for Jeffie here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.23,0:47:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今认识了你那是好上加好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Even more so now that he knows you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.39,0:47:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能给他带来好的影响  吉恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're a good influence, Gene.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.74,0:47:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧我这脑子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, where's my brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.12,0:47:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直忘了问你咬咬的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I keep forgetting to ask you about Nippy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.74,0:47:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬咬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nippy?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.03,0:47:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.81,0:47:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定不会相信的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're not gonna believe this,
